{"tid":1882540,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"1分鐘做21次「蛇行瑜珈招式」　印度11歲女童破世界紀錄","createTime":"2020-02-16T10:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T10:38:42.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7ed31961253e597040431608ba1706b54b0f9096","tid":1882540,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:18:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Oj7qdPx0YY0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOj7qdPx0YY0&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbpmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=cd66f138\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Oj7qdPx0YY0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NFrjxFWxilc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNFrjxFWxilc&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbpmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=bfa2afdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NFrjxFWxilc</a><br />\n<br />\n印度一名11歲的莉亞（Riya Paladia）日前在1分鐘內做完21次「Niralamba PoornaChakrasana」的高難度瑜珈招式，打破金氏世界紀錄，下一個目標是在奧運會奪得金牌。<br />\n <br />\n綜合印度媒體報導，北阿坎德邦（Uttarakhand）奈尼塔爾縣（Nainital）的村莊於上月20日舉行見證大會，莉亞在眾人的呼聲下完成21次「無支撐站立」，平躺在地板後沒有借助任何手的力量站起來，這個動作也被稱為做困難的瑜珈招式之一。<br />\n <br />\n莉亞的教練阿密特（Amit）表示，莉亞一直很熱衷於體操跟瑜珈，平日花3至5個小時訓練，假日則可以達到7至8個小時，之後會朝著奧運金牌的目標努力。<br />\n <br />\n網友看了影片紛紛表示，「這是循環播放嗎？」、「能完成這個動作很了不起」、「快打給驅魔人！」、「這是蛇吧」。"},{"pid":"d2039bf30d29f807705b89284330151a5dad7577","tid":1882540,"uid":93649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:19:20.000Z","msg":"條女係印度好危險..."},{"pid":"0f1cb1eb768c02cc02c17af773054dd2c1482b7c","tid":1882540,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2039bf30d29f807705b89284330151a5dad7577","tid":1882540,"uid":93649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:19:20.000Z","msg":"條女係印度好危險..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:19:56.000Z","msg":"Why"},{"pid":"bc9b2cb2df0202ec6b03566411e0284fafbcfbc8","tid":1882540,"uid":46587,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score